a_N:=\sup_{x\in\mathbb R}\left|\sum_{|n|\geq N}e^{-(x+n)^2}\right|=\sup_x\sum_{n\geq N}e^{-(x+n)^2}+\sum_{n\leq -N}e^{-(x+n)^2}\geq\sup_x\sum_{n\geq N}e^{-(x+n)^2}
a_N\geq\sup_x\sum_{n\geq 0}e^{-(x+N+n)^2}\geq \sup_x\sum_{n\geq 0}e^{-(x+n)^2}\geq \sum_{n\geq 0}e^{-n^2}\geq 1.
